---
title: Pork & Rosemary Pie with Parmesan Mash Topping & Balsamic Salad
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped
number. It's just like Nonna used to make (but better!).
